data.name: labInfo.Text
data.value:
Please fill out the Boxes on the left and click save to create a new Config.
To use the Screenshare program you need a WiFi-enabled microcontroller to drive the WS2812b LED matrix. It is recommended to use a ESP32 Board. if you haven't configured the ESP already please download the Arduino code and configure your WiFi credentials as well as the Size of your Matrix.
The Windows application will configure the Matrix-size automatically after a connection to the ESP is established.
